<codeline><highlight class="normal">XML<sp/>document<sp/>through<sp/>an<sp/>XSL<sp/>processor<sp/>and<sp/>save<sp/>the<sp/>result<sp/>as<sp/>an<sp/>HTML<sp/>file<sp/>in</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">the<sp/>same<sp/>directory.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">####<sp/>Printing</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Firefox<sp/>is<sp/>the<sp/>best<sp/>browser<sp/>to<sp/>use<sp/>if<sp/>you<sp/>need<sp/>to<sp/>print<sp/>your<sp/>specification.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Tests<sp/>done<sp/>on<sp/>Safari<sp/>and<sp/>Chrome<sp/>have<sp/>shown<sp/>that<sp/>the<sp/>page<sp/>dimensions<sp/>are<sp/>not</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">calculated<sp/>correctly.<sp/>As<sp/>a<sp/>result,<sp/>you<sp/>may<sp/>see<sp/>that<sp/>the<sp/>table<sp/>of<sp/>contents</highlight></codeline>
